back\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 29, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104itv1719677836442.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/itv1719677836442.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/itv1719677836442.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ikp1665702597787\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $instanceparent\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ikp1665702597787___instanceparent_270019\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the name of the parent instance of the specified component instance.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__topic_d84713e1_d84714e1_d84715e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__p_d84716e1_d84717e1_d84718e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instanceparent</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__topic_d56142e1_d56143e1_d56144e1_d56145e1_d56146e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d984847e75\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__d6052e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__d6052e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__d6052e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__d6052e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__d6052e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__d6052e20__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__d6052e20__entry__3\">Name of component instance; optional. If\n\t\t\t\t omitted, the current instance is used. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__topic_d56147e1_d56148e1_d56149e1_d56150e1_d56151e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d984847e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__li_d34556e1_d34557e1_d34558e1\">Name of the parent instance of <var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var> when:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__li_d34559e1_d34560e1_d34561e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var> is a modal form instance that is not started from the apStart trigger.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__li_d34562e1_d34563e1_d34564e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var> is an attached, non-modal component instance. (A detached, non-modal component instance has no parent.)\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__li_d34565e1_d34566e1_d34567e1\">Empty string (\"\"), in the following circumstances:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__li_d34568e1_d34569e1_d34570e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var> is a child of the application screen. For example, <var class=\"keyword varname\">InstName</var> is a detached, non-modal form instance or is a modal form instance started from the apStart trigger.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__li_d34571e1_d34572e1_d34573e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var> is running on a server and its parent is running on the client. In this case, <var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var> is considered to be a child of the application screen that belongs to the Application Server application.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__li_d34574e1_d34575e1_d34576e1\">An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following this\n            Function</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__2\"> Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__3\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-57 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__3\"> The named instance cannot be found in the\n\t\t\t\t component pool. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_FIELD&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__3\"> An incorrect field name was provided;\n\t\t\t\t either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component.\n\t\t\t\t </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1105 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_INSTANCE&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__3\"> The instance name provided is not valid.\n\t\t\t\t For example, the argument contains incorrect characters. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ryt1665702577808.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryt1665702577808.html\" title=\"Creates a new instance of a component.\">newinstance</a>.\n                             </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1304 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_UNKNOWN_CONTEXT&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ikp1665702597787__table_d8840e1_d8841e1_d8842e1__entry__3\"> Function not allowed, unknown context.\n\t\t\t\t The <var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var> argument was omitted and one of the following occurred: <p class=\"p\">There is no current instance, for\n\t\t\t\t example, in the apStart trigger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The current instance is a form started\n\t\t\t\t with <code class=\"ph codeph\">run</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__topic_d56152e1_d56153e1_d56154e1_d56155e1_d56156e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d984847e340\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__p_d84728e1_d84729e1_d84730e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__section_fft_v4z_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d984847e350\">Example: Reporting the Parent of the Current Instance </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example reports the current instance's parent in the\n               message frame:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ikp1665702597787__pre_vmg_z4z_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">putmess \"%%$instanceparent is the parent of %%$instancename\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryt1665702577808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>newinstance</a><p>Creates a new instance of a component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dnh1719419352908.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$detachedinstances</a><p>Return a list of detached instances.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bgv1665702597635.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancechildren</a><p>Return a list of component instances attached to a specified component instance.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7421428\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7421428\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$instanceparent Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 29, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $instanceparent Return the name of the parent instance of the specified component instance. $instanceparent { ( InstanceName ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description InstanceName String Name of component instance; optional. If omitted, the current instance is used. Return Values Name of the parent instance of InstanceName when: InstanceName is a modal form instance that is not started from the apStart trigger. InstanceName is an attached, non-modal component instance. (A detached, non-modal component instance has no parent.) Empty string (\"\"), in the following circumstances: InstanceName is a child of the application screen. For example, InstName is a detached, non-modal form instance or is a modal form instance started from the apStart trigger. InstanceName is running on a server and its parent is running on the client. In this case, InstanceName is considered to be a child of the application screen that belongs to the Application Server application. An error occurred. $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following this Function Value Error constant Meaning -57 <UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE> The named instance cannot be found in the component pool. -1101 <UPROCERR_FIELD> An incorrect field name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component. -1105 <UPROCERR_INSTANCE> The instance name provided is not valid. For example, the argument contains incorrect characters. For more information, see newinstance . -1304 <UPROCERR_UNKNOWN_CONTEXT> Function not allowed, unknown context. The InstanceName argument was omitted and one of the following occurred: There is no current instance, for example, in the apStart trigger. The current instance is a form started with run . Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Reporting the Parent of the Current Instance The following example reports the current instance's parent in the message frame: putmess \"%%$instanceparent is the parent of %%$instancename\" Copy Related Links newinstance Creates a new instance of a component. $detachedinstances Return a list of detached instances. $instancechildren Return a list of component instances attached to a specified component instance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}